title: What's the catchiest LoL parody song?
body:
Which one always gets stuck in your head and never, ever, ever leaves?

Never, ever, ever... http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GLo3AUdZUkE

I have never heard this before. This is awesome. Thanks for sharing!

I was hoping when I was looking through this someone would have posted this. Good job sir.

How has no one said this one? 

We Are Never Ever Going to Lane Together: 
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GLo3AUdZUkE&feature=youtu.be

I'll Quit LoL:

I use the "We Are Never Ever Going to Lane Together" whenever I'm showing people not familiar with LoL how awesome the community is. Totally incomprehensible to them, but they know the song, so they grok it easily. Looove it.

Easily "PWN your Face".

http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Zf9VSDt0EN4
This is always the first thing I think of when I think "League of Legends parody song".

I'm personally fond of ThePopushi's cover of Trouble! I still to this day can't get it out of my head.

http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=t_Mk_bBW3uM

I love Sandy/ThePopushi as well! Her "We Are Never Ever Going To Lane Together" is remarkably nostalgic of my early days supporting.

That would be my favorite. Although, Hotshotgg and Saint in "I Just Played Jax" made the video really enjoyable. XD

http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IdWnVfXDrW0

Nothing will ever beat this. Best song ever.
